==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Airman
<hw>Air"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A man who
ascends or flies in an aircraft; an aviator; an airplane
pilot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>an enlisted man in the air force; there are several
grades.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Airmanship</ent>⟦br⟧
